data.description: this home is in a most desirable neighborhood . close to exit 7 near every thing. i like the new up grades and the new look of the house.beautify home in excellent location and is priced right .
data.whatILove: i love the new updates  and remodeling that has just been completed . new cabinets, stainless steel appliances, all hardwood floors in living room, hallway and master bedroom has been refinished and are beautiful . new carpet in two bedroom  tile in both bathrooms. beautiful huge den down stairs with  tile floors leading out side to a nice deck with beautiful landscaping .also two car drive under garage . house has been newly painted inside and outside.
